text: Today on @realmoney @dougkass @SeabreezeLP Dec 02, 2022 | 08:39 AM EST DOUG KASS More on Group Stink, Errant Consensus Market Forecasts and My Developing Market View * 2022 was a year in which too many demonstrated dogma and lack of flexibility/objectivity.
